# ========================================
# Agent-memory created by subagents in subdirectories
# Backup files
# Claude Code Internals (DO NOT COMMIT)
# Copilot tracking (local-only, never commit)
# Database (local runtime data, never commit)
# Debug and cache
# Editor files
# Host-specific runtime configs (only .example is tracked)
# LaTeX build artifacts
# Logs
# Node modules
# OS files
# Package lock (not needed for this config repo)
# Python cache
# Research report outputs (generated files, never commit)
# Runtime state
# Rust build artifacts
# Secrets
# Session data
# Telemetry and analytics
# Temp files
# Test results and reports
